auty, Makeup, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('135', '4', 'SQUA BALANCING GEL', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;A light-textured Squalane gel protects moisture within skin to last long till next morning. Rose apple leaf extract and Gold seaweed extract create the best balance of moisture and oil on skin and even out the skin tone. You will have a dewy yet refreshing afterfeel, letting makeup intact longer. No greasy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;How to use: After you hydrate the skin with toner fully, take 2 or 3 red bean-size and mix by both hands to apply to whole face softly. Adjust the volume depending on skin condition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'A light-textured Squalane gel protects moisture within skin to last long till next morning. Rose apple leaf extract and Gold seaweed extract create the best balance of moisture and oil on skin and even out the skin tone...', 'Squa balancing gel, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'Squa balancing gel, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('136', '2', 'SQUA DEW', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Refreshing Squalane water. Squalane and other moisturizing ingredients make an instant barrier on skin against dryness. Spray bottle allows an easy application. Good for those with oily skin or those who love a light afterfeel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;How to use: After you hydrate the skin with toner fully, spray over your face. One or more pushing, depending on your skin condition. Blend on skin by both hands pressing on face softly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Refreshing Squalane water. Squalane and other moisturizing ingredients make an instant barrier on skin against dryness. Spray bottle allows an easy application. Good for those with oily skin or those who love a light afterfeel...', 'Squa Dew, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'Squa Dew, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('118', '4', 'SQUA FACIAL FOAM', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;A well-lathering facial foam containing Squalane and silk powder, makes skin smooth and moisturized after washing. Creamy foam like whipped cream absorbs dirt in pores softly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;How to use: Apply 1-2 cm to lather with water or lukewarm water well. Wash softly as if wrap your face with foam.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'A well-lathering facial foam containing Squalane and silk powder, makes skin smooth and moisturized after washing. Creamy foam like whipped cream absorbs dirt in pores softly. ', 'Squa facial foam, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'Squa facial foam, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('141', '4', 'UV PROTECT 15', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Skin-friendly creamy sunscreen with UV scattering agents blocks ultraviolet rays for everyday use. It smoothes out well on skin and hard to be come off by sweat. Squalane in the formula moisturizes skin while no use of UV absorbing agents is safe to sensitive skin holders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;How to use: After your skin-care, apply a thin layer over the skin. Repeat the application not to miss any part being bare to sunlight.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Skin-friendly creamy sunscreen with UV scattering agents blocks ultraviolet rays for everyday use. It smoothes out well on skin and hard to be come off by sweat...', 'Uv protect 15, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'Uv protect 15, Haba, Supplement, Thực phẩm chức năng, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('174', '4', 'Very Gentle Cleansing Cream', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(255, 0, 153)&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pdt-desc-pod&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Soothe and protect the weakened skin barrier and care for easily irritated skin with our most gentle cleanser. Thoroughly removes impurities and make-up (including eye make-up) to leave&amp;nbsp;skin feeling soft, soothed and beautifully refreshed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Fragrance free, essential oil free and dermatologically tested. You&amp;rsquo;re in safe hands.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;How to apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Gently massage onto damp skin on face, neck and d&amp;eacute;colletage. Rinse with warm water using a face cloth for best results. Use daily or as often as required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Ingredients&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Aqua (water), Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Caprylic/capric triglyceride, Cetearyl alcohol, Cetearyl olivate (and) sorbitan olivate, Phragmites kharka extract and (water) (and) poria cocos extract, Camellia oleifera seed oil, Persea gratissima, Chamomilla recutita flower extract, Olea europaea fruit oil, Oenothera biennis seed oil, Camellia sinensis leaf extract, Calendula officinalis flower extract (and) glycine soja (soybean) oil, Rosmarinus officinalis leaf extract, Xanthan gum, Citric acid, Dehydroacetic acid (and) benzyl alcohol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;From time to time minor changes may occur to this ingredient list. Always refer to the product packaging.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Soothe and protect the weakened skin barrier and care for easily irritated skin with our most gentle cleanser. Thoroughly removes impurities and make-up (including eye make-up) to leave skin feeling soft, soothed and beautifully refreshed...', 'Very Gentle Cleansing Cream, Trilogy, Makeup, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'Very Gentle Cleansing Cream, Trilogy, Makeup, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('177', '4', 'Cream Cleanser (200ml)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(255, 0, 153)&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;This simple one-step cleanser does more than just remove make-up and impurities from face and eyes. Non-drying, it leaves skin feeling smoother, softer and beautifully refreshed.&amp;nbsp; It&amp;#39;s your perfect preparation morning and night.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;How to apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Gently massage onto damp skin on face, neck and d&amp;eacute;colletage.&amp;nbsp; Tissue off or rinse with warm water (using a face cloth for best results).&amp;nbsp; Use daily or as often as required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Ingredients&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Aqua (water), Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Glycerin (vegetable), Rosa Canina (rosehip) seed oil, Cetearyl olivate (and) sorbitan olivate, Cetearyl alcohol, Oenothera biennis seed oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Tocopheryl acetate, Aloe barbadenis leaf extract, Daucus carota sativa seed oil, Chamomilla recutita flower extract, Citrus auranitum amara flower oil, Xanthan gum, Citric acid, Dehydroacetic acid (and) benzyl alcohol, Rosmarinus officinalis leaf extract, Parfum, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, Limonene, Linalool&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;From time to time minor changes may occur to this ingredient list. Always refer to the product packaging.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'K