Liquid Foundation vừa c&amp;oacute; chức năng l&amp;agrave;m lớp nền trang điểm cơ bản, vừa tạo th&amp;agrave;nh một lớp m&amp;agrave;ng chống tia UV vững chắc.Nhờ v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh phần tự nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Liquid Foundation hầu như kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&amp;acirc;y k&amp;iacute;ch ứng, dị ứng da.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0066&quot;&gt;Hướng dẫn sử dụng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Lắc nhẹ, đều trước khi sử dụng. Lấy một lượng vừa đủ ra đầu ng&amp;oacute;n tay hoặc b&amp;ocirc;ng trang điểm rồi xoa đều l&amp;ecirc;n mặt.&amp;nbsp;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng để trong ph&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;oacute; nhiệt độ qu&amp;aacute; cao hoặc hơi tiếp x&amp;uacute;c trực tiếp với &amp;aacute;nh nắng mặt trời.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0066&quot;&gt;Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&amp;acirc;̀n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Chiết xuất tinh chất gạo được sản xuất trong nước Nhật, bột chất kho&amp;aacute;ng thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n.&amp;nbsp;Cam kết kh&amp;ocirc;ng sử dụng h&amp;oacute;a chất bảo quản cũng như chất tạo m&amp;agrave;u, m&amp;ugrave;i.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hạn sử dụng&amp;nbsp;3 năm trước khi mở nắp. 6 th&amp;aacute;ng sau khi mở nắp.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` VALUES ('194', '4', 'CoQ10 Booster Oil', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(255, 0, 153)&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Newly certified organic oil blend formulated with our latest innovation Glycablend&amp;trade; for supple, healthy, radiant skin at any age. Intensively nourishing, CoQ10 Booster Oil recharges and revitalises skin at a cellular level, boosting collagen and elastin production and protecting against free radical damage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Tamanu, macadamia and black caraway seed oils plus antioxidant co-enzyme Q10 help feed and renew skin. Glycablend&amp;trade;, a potent blend of chia, blueberry, strawberry and pomegranate oils, keeps skin supple and youthful.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;A seriously addictive addition to any skincare regime, this potent formulation assists super-fast skin recovery, giving dull and lacklustre skin a renewed radiance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;How to apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Gently massage 2-3 drops into cleansed face, neck and decolletage. &amp;nbsp;Apply morning and/or night. Use alone or before applying moisturising products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#ff0099&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Ingredients&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Macadamia ternifolia seed oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Tocopheryl acetate, Nigella sativa, Calophyllum Tacamahaca (Tamanu) Seed Oil, Ubiquinone, Euterpe oleracea fruit oil, Lecithin, Parfum, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, Limonene, Linalool&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;From time to time minor changes may occur to this ingredient list. Always refer to the product packaging.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Newly certified organic oil blend formulated with our latest innovation Glycablend™ for supple, healthy, radiant skin at any age. Intensively nourishing, CoQ10 Booster Oil recharges and revitalises skin at a cellular level...', 'CoQ10 Booster Serum, Trilogy, Makeup, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp', 'CoQ10 Booster Serum, Trilogy, Makeup, Làm đẹp, Chăm sóc da, Mỹ phẩm, Kem dưỡng ẩm, Sản phẩm làm đẹp');
